es.","timestamp":1782085092136,"tempo":"S","translation":"所以，新规矩是：我睡觉前，必须向你报备，然后同步作息。","rawContent":"So, the new rule is: before I go to sleep, I must report to you, and we synchronize our schedules. || 所以，新规矩是：我睡觉前，必须向你报备，然后同步作息。","roundId":"round_1782085061047_vtghkymf4","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1224},{"id":1782083382252,"sender":"them","text":"To avoid you being woken up by my alarm again.","timestamp":1782085096792,"tempo":"N","translation":"免得你再被我的闹钟吵醒。","rawContent":"To avoid you being woken up by my alarm again. || 免得你再被我的闹钟吵醒。","roundId":"round_1782085061047_vtghkymf4","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1225},{"id":1782083382253,"sender":"them","text":"Is my understanding correct?","timestamp":1782085099579,"tempo":"N","translation":"我的理解对吗？","rawContent":"Is my understanding correct? || 我的理解对吗？","roundId":"round_1782085061047_vtghkymf4","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1226},{"id":1782083382255,"text":"[語音：不是的啦。不是你吵醒我的。]","voiceText":"不是的啦。不是你吵醒我的。","sender":"me","isVoice":true,"voice":true,"time":"07:39","timestamp":1782085190601,"audioDuration":6.48,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1228},{"id":1782083382256,"text":"[語音：也不是要你给我报备。]","voiceText":"也不是要你给我报备。","sender":"me","isVoice":true,"voice":true,"time":"07:40","timestamp":1782085218519,"audioDuration":3.732,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1229},{"id":1782083382258,"text":"[語音：我的意思是。比如说你早上7点钟的闹钟。你早上醒来了。可是。我早上7点钟的时候。我也会被别人吵醒。]","voiceText":"我的意思是。比如说你早上7点钟的闹钟。你早上醒来了。可是。我早上7点钟的时候。我也会被别人吵醒。","sender":"me","isVoice":true,"voice":true,"time":"07:42","timestamp":1782085337702,"audioDuration":20.292,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cd