ind of low-consumption state.","timestamp":1782085564458,"tempo":"N","translation":"我的作息数年如一日，作为学者，体力消耗也小。身体会适应这种低耗能状态。","rawContent":"My routine has barely changed for years. As a scholar, my physical exertion is minimal. The body adapts to this kind of low-consumption state. || 我的作息数年如一日，作为学者，体力消耗也小。身体会适应这种低耗能状态。","roundId":"round_1782085525463_e97y0lc1k","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1237},{"id":1782083382266,"sender":"them","text":"And, the body's memory for pain is quite honest.","timestamp":1782085567393,"tempo":"N","translation":"而且，身体对于疼痛的记忆是很诚实的。","rawContent":"And, the body's memory for pain is quite honest. || 而且，身体对于疼痛的记忆是很诚实的。","roundId":"round_1782085525463_e97y0lc1k","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1238},{"id":1782083382267,"sender":"them","text":"The plan to sleep earlier is a sensible one.","timestamp":1782085570353,"tempo":"S","translation":"早睡的计划是明智的。","rawContent":"The plan to sleep earlier is a sensible one. || 早睡的计划是明智的。","roundId":"round_1782085525463_e97y0lc1k","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1239},{"id":1782083382268,"text":"是她打来的，看来我们昨晚关于作息的讨论还有后续。","content":"是她打来的，看来我们昨晚关于作息的讨论还有后续。","sender":"them","type":"thought","time":"07:46","timestamp":1782085606397,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":1240},{"id":1782085940721,"sender":"me","content":"視頻通話已結束，通話時長 5分25秒","text":"視頻通話已結束，通話時長 5分25秒\n\n[System Note: Call Summary (5分25秒)]\n使用者早起後向Al haitham抱怨全身酸痛與頭痛，Al haitham觀察到其不適，建議沖熱水澡或做簡單拉伸，並指出僵硬與頭痛是休息不足的反應。使用者接受建議，決定先去喝溫水再行動。Al haitham表示會在旁觀察結果，對話在平靜的關懷氣氛中結束。","timestamp":"2026-06-21T23:52:20.721Z","isVideoCallLog":true,"callStatus":"connected","callDuration":325,"callLogId":"call_1782085606403_jqgp8h","isSummarizing":false,"callSummary":"使用者早起後向Al haitham抱怨全身酸痛與頭痛，Al haitham觀察到其不適，建議沖熱水澡